---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about who I am and what I do"
	pubDate={new Date()}
>
	<h2>👋 About Me</h2>
	
	<p>
		Hello! I'm <strong>[Your Name]</strong>, a [your role] based in [your location]. 
		I'm passionate about [your passions] and love to [what you enjoy doing].
	</p>
	
	<p>
		[Write a paragraph about your background, experience, and what drives you. 
		This is your chance to tell your story and connect with visitors.]
	</p>
	
	<h2>💼 Experience</h2>
	
	<div class="timeline">
		<div class="timeline-item">
			<h3>[Job Title] @ [Company]</h3>
			<p class="date">[Start Date] - [End Date/Present]</p>
			<p>[Brief description of your role and achievements]</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="timeline-item">
			<h3>[Job Title] @ [Company]</h3>
			<p class="date">[Start Date] - [End Date]</p>
			<p>[Brief description of your role and achievements]</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<h2>🛠️ Skills</h2>
	
	<div class="skills">
		<span class="skill-tag">[Skill 1]</span>
		<span class="skill-tag">[Skill 2]</span>
		<span class="skill-tag">[Skill 3]</span>
		<span class="skill-tag">[Skill 4]</span>
		<span class="skill-tag">[Skill 5]</span>
		<span class="skill-tag">[Skill 6]</span>
	</div>
	
	<h2>📚 Education</h2>
	
	<div class="education">
		<h3>[Degree] in [Major]</h3>
		<p>[University Name] | [Graduation Year]</p>
	</div>
	
	<h2>🏆 Achievements</h2>
	
	<ul>
		<li>[Achievement 1 - e.g., Award, certification, notable project]</li>
		<li>[Achievement 2]</li>
		<li>[Achievement 3]</li>
	</ul>
	
	<h2>📬 Let's Connect</h2>
	
	<p>
		I'm always interested in hearing about new projects and opportunities. 
		Whether you have a question or just want to say hi, feel free to reach out!
	</p>
	
	<p>
		📧 Email: <a href="mailto:[your-email]">[your-email]</a><br/>
		💼 LinkedIn: <a href="[linkedin-url]">[Your Profile]</a><br/>
		🐙 GitHub: <a href="[github-url]">[Your Profile]</a><br/>
		🐦 Twitter: <a href="[twitter-url]">[Your Profile]</a>
	</p>
</Layout>

<style>
	.timeline {
		margin: 1.5em 0;
	}
	.timeline-item {
		padding: 1em 0;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
		padding-left: 1.5em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	.timeline-item h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.25em 0;
	}
	.timeline-item .date {
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.9em;
		margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
	}
	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5em;
		margin: 1em 0;
	}
	.skill-tag {
		background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
		padding: 0.25em 0.75em;
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-size: 0.9em;
	}
	.education {
		margin: 1em 0;
	}
	a {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
</style>
